            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is beginning to soften, increase the heat to high, then add the <strong>chopped chicken</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until browned all over</p><p>Once the chicken has browned, reduce the heat to medium high, then add the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and your <strong>curry powder</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
